  m_Name: BrotherJournal_04
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 39
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD anh trai #4 \u2014 L\u1EDDi t\u1EF1 th\xFA cu\u1ED1i c\xF9ng"
  category: 2
  content: "N\u1EBFu ai t\xECm th\u1EA5y cu\u1ED1n nh\u1EADt k\xFD n\xE0y, ngh\u0129a
    l\xE0 m\xECnh \u0111\xE3 th\u1EA5t b\u1EA1i. M\xECnh \u0111\xE3 c\u1ED1 g\u1EAFng
    ki\u1EC3m so\xE1t con qu\xE1i v\u1EADt b\xEAn trong m\xECnh, nh\u01B0ng n\xF3
    ng\xE0y c\xE0ng m\u1EA1nh h\u01A1n. M\xECnh kh\xF4ng mu\u1ED1n l\xE0m h\u1EA1i
    ai, \u0111\u1EB7c bi\u1EC7t l\xE0 em trai m\xECnh. M\xECnh \u0111\xE3 gi\u1EA5u
    b\u1ED9 k\xEDch n\u1ED5 \u1EDF t\u1EA7ng tr\xEAn c\xF9ng. N\u1EBFu m\xECnh bi\u1EBFn
    th\xE0nh con qu\xE1i v\u1EADt \u0111\xF3 ho\xE0n to\xE0n, h\xE3y k\xEDch n\u1ED5
    qu\u1EA3 bom. \u0110\xF3 l\xE0 c\xE1ch duy nh\u1EA5t \u0111\u1EC3 d\u1EADp t\u1EAFt
    d\u1ECBch b\u1EC7nh. M\xECnh xin l\u1ED7i, em."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
